{"tid":1667004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣無水？","createTime":"2019-10-21T08:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:25:35.000Z","uid":192585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"520d048a0c1b2aa4dff2bb9128facbd817ba60aa","tid":1667004,"uid":192585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"荃灣無水？"},{"pid":"7cbee7e3e3f86e14407d96dcd2e6df35b16b949b","tid":1667004,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"2afe61d4189233e85c2206c7e82bb8c00ab09fb6","tid":1667004,"uid":167503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"成個荃灣都無食水 好似係"},{"pid":"8116e98b476da3641460beccaec647c51c0feae0","tid":1667004,"uid":192585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"荃灣仲有邊度有水"},{"pid":"6ad96f289d48aec098e1e6dc54a71be4d8f9432d","tid":1667004,"uid":114064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"共產狗停水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0b5e01679f6dc1c487c8c0a688f3ba2c6b82f3","tid":1667004,"uid":192585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"48dee72a618b6c641a973524d98c6f532fd71630","tid":1667004,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"#區選要贏 #光復荃灣<br />\n<br />\n有冇荃灣人係屋企可以幫手睇下有冇食水，聽聞好多地方都突然冇左食水，已知荃灣街市(街市街)，石圍角，荃灣廣場，荃新天地一期<br />\n<br />\n唔想開名可以dm我，感謝🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n部分fc<br />\n部分地區包括石圍角，荃廣開始恢復供水，水流緩慢。"},{"pid":"474918d00b4f53aa51c60a8a3b7da1e4fd047eeb","tid":1667004,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"14ec3e6491cdc346d377e55aee70526918db5c8c","tid":1667004,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d423db6515dfa13991d5326a4608c220368b02bd","tid":1667004,"uid":72334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"收到管理處通知話得番最後一缸水<br />\n利申：荃豐果邊"},{"pid":"cdb4506708678de21d2e5b52f9d4209c27334fd4","tid":1667004,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"荃灣係藍區，D 藍屍廢老有乜嘢講？"},{"pid":"aac57298e0e6fb51081615e03eff5c12cc14632c","tid":1667004,"uid":299937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}